#. module: wine_merchant
#: model_terms:event.event,description:wine_merchant.event_event_2
msgid ""
"This class is perfect for anyone interested in wine, whether you’re a novice"
" looking to learn the basics or a seasoned enthusiast wanting to deepen your"
" knowledge. No prior experience is necessary!"
msgstr ""
